  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.1.11">
<l>karavicum perivaḷi nīrnila mivaimicai</l>
<l>varaṉavi ṟiṟalvali yaḷipoṟai yāyniṉṟa</l>
<l>paraṉaṭi mēlkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉco</l>
<l>ṉiraṉiṟai yāyirat tivaipattum vīṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>These ten in the thousand arranged in a row</l>
<l>spoken by Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr on the feet of the Highest</l>
<l>who stood as a mountain of god-uttering(?)  power, strength [and] care</l>
<l>in these: bright(?)  sky, fire, wind, water [and] ground,</l>
	<l>[mean] liberation.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
